description: Protect over a third of Jersey’s waters from mobile fishing through a Marine Park, champion local low-impact fisheries and communicate the Park’s value and impact to the general public.
Sustainable, low impact fisheries are championed within the Berwickshire MPA and research and management recommendations to ban mobile fishing within the MPA is considered by Marine Scotland.
1.5 million people engage with Blue Marine's educational initiatives.
Enable marine conservation to happen fast and effectively.
